    "text": "Protecting and Transforming Cyber Health Care Act of 2022 or the PATCH Act of 2022\n\nThis bill requires premarket applications for cyber devices (i.e., medical devices that include software or connect to the internet) to include information relating to cybersecurity, including plans to monitor for cybersecurity risks and address vulnerabilities through regular product updates."
